To run:

./run

=========
Dependencies:

OpenAL
SDL
SDL_image
python2.7

OpenSuse12.1:
sudo zypper install openal libpng12-0 libGLEW1_6 libSDL_image-1_2-0

Fedora16:
sudo rpm install openal SDL_image

Ubuntu11.10:
sudo apt-get install libopenal libsdl libsdl-image libglew

==============
Notes:

You will need gfx drivers with OpenGL version >=2.1
This information can be found using glxinfo

Turn off mouse acceleration for better controls
